he succeed terrence d. daniels , formerly a w.r. grace vice chairman , who resign .
w.r. grace hold three of grace energy 's seven board seat .
mcdermott international inc. say its babcock & wilcox unit complete the sale of its bailey control operation to finmeccanica s.p . a. for $ 295 million .
finmeccanica be an italian state - own hold company with interest in the mechanical engineer industry .
bailey control , based in wickliffe , ohio , make computerize industrial control system .
it employ 2,700 people and have annual revenue of about $ 370 million .
the federal government suspend sale of u.s. savings bond because congress have n't lift the ceiling on government debt .
until congress act , the government have n't any authority to issue new debt obligation of any kind , the treasury say .
the government 's borrow authority drop at midnight tuesday to $ 2.80 trillion from $ 2.87 trillion .
legislation to lift the debt ceiling be ensnarled in the fight over cut capital - gain tax .
the house have vote to raise the ceiling to $ 3.1 trillion , but the senate be n't expect to act until next week at the earliest .
the treasury say the u.s. will default on nov. 9 if congress do n't act by then .
