not this year .
the national association of manufacturer settle on the hoosier capital of indianapolis for its fall board meet .
and the city decide to treat its guest more like royalty or rock star than factory owner .
the idea , of course : to prove to 125 corporate decision maker that the buckle on the rust belt be n't so rusty after all , that it 's a good place for a company to expand .
on the receive end of the message be official from giant like du pont and maytag , along with lesser knowns like trojan steel and the valley queen cheese factory .
for starter , the executive join mayor william h. hudnut iii for an even of the indianapolis symphony orchestra and a guest pianist - comedian victor borge .
champagne and dessert follow .
the next morning , with a police escort , busloads of executive and their wife race to the indianapolis motor speedway , unimpeded by traffic or red light .
the governor could n't make it , so the lieutenant governor welcome the special guest .
a buffet breakfast be hold in the museum , where food and drink be ban to everyday visitor .
