dmitry medvedev be impress by the weapon and the level of train .
dmitry medvedev also state that it be good that the military be get new missile like the topol @-@ m .
missile from the base in teikovo take part in the victory day parade on may 9 , 2008 when russia display the country 's military hardware on red square in moscow for the first time since the soviet collapse .
dmitry medvedev experience motivation while watch the missile across the square and promise that such parade will continue and may be expand in the future .
dmitry medvedev state that the russian federation 's task for the next few year be to make sure that the strategic missile force receive the necessary fund to respond to modern threat .
dmitry medvedev also state that certain progress have be make recently and that the speed of progress must not be lose .
dmitry medvedev promise to raise officer ' salary .
dmitry medvedev be swear in on may 7 , 2008 as the russian federation 's president and have so far portray an image of a liberal and avoid the harsh anti @-@ western rhetoric of vladimir putin .
vladimir putin be dmitry medvedev 's predecessor and mentor .
most observer expect dmitry medvedev to continue the policy of vladimir putin , such as an assertive posture on the international scene and vow to strengthen the military .
teikovo be a small town in the ivanovo region about 250 kilometers or 155 mile northeast of moscow .
vladimir putin fiercely oppose the unite state ' plan to deploy missile defense site in poland and the czech republic , and nato 's plan to accept into the alliance russia 's ex @-@ soviet neighbors , ukraine and georgia .
vladimir putin have threaten to point nuclear missile at country that take part in u.s. missile defense and opted out of a key soviet @-@ era arm control treaty .
topol @-@ m missile be capable of hit target more than 10000 kilometers or 6000 mile away .
the missile be deploy in both silo @-@ based and truck @-@ mount version .
strategic missile force chief general nikolai solovtsov state that the topol @-@ m be a new step in missile design .
vladimir putin and other official have boast about the topol @-@ m 's ability to penetrate any prospective missile defense .
yuri solomonov design the missile and state that the missile drop engine at a significantly lower altitude than earlier design which make it hard for an enemy 's early warn system to detect the launch .
yuri solomonov state that the missile ' warhead and decoy closely resemble one another in flight , make it very difficult for a foe to select the real target from a multitude of false one .
deployment of topol=ms have proceed slowly .
large oil revenue in recent year have allow the government of the russia federation to buy weapon and fund the development of new missile .
soviet @-@ built ballistic missile have remain the backbone of the nation 's nuclear force .
the navy of the russian federation be in poor shape .
soviet @-@ built nuclear submarine frequently need repair and rarely leave the base .
the yuri dolgoruky be the first in a series of new nuclear submarine to be commission this year but the bulava nuclear @-@ arm missile develop to equip the submarine have fail test and the deployment prospect be uncertain .
