great britain , japan , australia , argentina , costa rica , kenya and finland have be lead proponent of the treaty regulate the global arm trade .
great britain be a 3 billion unite state dollar per year arm exporter .
the treaty regulate the global arm trade would apply only to arm sale among nation and not commercial sale involve individual .
decision would require a simple majority .
john duncan state that the treaty regulate the global arm trade have to be as universal as possible and that some the country be arm manufacturer and that all nation be arm supplier at one stage or another .
john duncan state that it be by closing loophole that nation can stop arm distribution into the hand of criminal and terrorist .
john duncan be great britain 's ambassador for multilateral arm control and disarmament .
