christina rocca make this statement to other nation assemble for the vote on move ahead with the treaty regulate the global arm trade .
in 061200 the unite state cast the sole dissent vote when 153 nation vote in support of consider the creation of a treaty regulate the global arm trade .
the 061200 vote set in motion the process of consider an arm trade treaty .
that process include meeting from 071031 to 081031 among a group of expert that recommend item for consideration that include the consensus language .
the 081031 vote will move forward arm trade treaty discussion toward the specific of the possible language of the arm trade treaty .
christina rocca state that the unite state support the goal of promote responsibility in arm transfer and reduce the destabilizing trade in illicit arm .
christina rocca state that the unite state do not believe a global arm trade treaty would accomplish the promotion of responsibility in arm transfer and the reduction of the destabilizing trade in illicit arm .
christina rocca state that the only way to convince all major arm export country to sign on to the arm trade treaty would be to weaken the arm trade treaty provision and a weak arm trade treaty would legitimize an international standard based on a low common denominator that would not address the problem of illicit and irresponsible arm transfer .
