this would make it futile to give the csbc the capacity to build them .
the unite state have control of the key technology in build the submarine .
lee wen @-@ chung be another dpp legislator who have be involve .
lee say on 040628 that the delegation ask the unite state to shorten the delivery period of the submarine from 15 year to 10 year .
this indicate that taiwan have already give up the policy of build the submarine itself .
