chinese official state that the geostationary satellite will provide communication service over africa and part of the middle east and southern europe .
the chinese official also state that the satellite will go into operation by the end of 2007 and be expect to last 15 year .
the satellite will be manage from a control station in abuja , nigeria .
this launch mark the first time china have build a commercial satellite and put the satellite into orbit on contract for another country .
the launch occur on may 14 , 2007 before dawn near the xichang space center in southwestern sichuan province .
some view the launch as another sign of china 's increase skill in space technology and china 's determination to be among the world 's great power seek to utilize the reach of outer space for benefit on earth .
china 's space program 's rapid progress have cause worry in the unite state because the program be run by the military and china have be recently emphasize space @-@ based information warfare .
the concern intensify follow the successful january 11 , 2007 test @-@ fire of an anti @-@ satellite missile .
some analyst state that the test @-@ fire demonstrate a risk to the many satellite on which unite state military force rely for navigation and weapon guidance .
china 's space agency sent 2 astronaut into orbit in october 2005 in the agency 's second man spaceflight .
the chinese government on may 7 , 2007 adopt a 10 year plan for expand space exploration .
the plan include more man flight as well as unman probe of the moon and beyond .
chinese official state that the launch of the nigcomsat @-@ 1 aboard a long march 3 b rocket on may 14 , 2007 represent a commercial challenge .
some see the launch as a symbol of china 's broad network of economic relation with africa .
the official new china news agency state that the satellite represent china 's wish to cooperate with develop country in the peaceful use of outer space and to promote a close relationship between china and african country .
nigeria 's manage director of the nigcomsat @-@ 1 project ham rufai state that the launch be a breakthrough in end the exclusive reliance on oil because the satellite will help nigeria move toward knowledge @-@ based industry .
the official new china news agency state that china secure the 311 million dollar contract in 2004 in a bid process in which 21 other company take part .
president of the great wall industry corporation wang haibo state that the nigerian contract put china onto the short list of country that can build , launch and maintain a satellite for other nation .
chinese official state that about 30 similar contract have be sign for future launch .
in the 1990 s china frequently launch satellite for other country after the satellite be manufacture elsewhere and acquire a reputation for provide such service more cheaply than other launch @-@ capable country .
china have be try to establish commercial relation with oil @-@ produce nation such as nigeria as the chinese economy grow nearly 10 percent a year .
some official have state that nigeria hope to sell communication band to neighboring african country .
abuja be the capital of nigeria .
2007 @-@ 06 @-@ 09
mexico ( mx )
international ; crime ; war and conflict
at least 46 people be kill by the end of the week .
there be multiple attack include hand @-@ grenade assault and decapitation , with police , federal agent and rival drug @-@ trafficker the principal victim .
mexico 's drug @-@ traffic war continue during the funeral of a 10 @-@ year @-@ old boy .
the boy die in a drown accident unrelated to drug traffic .
the boy 's grandfather be miguel angel felix gallardo .
gallardo be the fugitive founder of the tijuana drug cartel .
june 4 , 2007 6 hood gunmen enter the traditional all @-@ night wake and shoot two people , kill both .
one newspaper call the gunmen commando .
the gunmen have write z 's on the victim ' back before the left .
the z be a symbol of the gulf cartel .
at least 46 more people be kill by the end of the week .
there be multiple attack include hand @-@ grenade assault and decapitation , with police , federal agent and rival drug @-@ trafficker the principal victim .
the killings show the scope of the violence and the tactic of psychological warfare behind it .
the killings be disperse across the country .
many death appear to involve dispute between compete band of trafficker .
at least one of those band appear to be split into different group .
authority in tuxtepec on june 5 , 2007 find a sever head with a note .
the note state that this be go to happen to all the people who work with the zetas .
it referred to the hit men who work for the gulf cartel .
the message be sign as the new blood .
tuxtepec be in the southeast side of oaxaca .
the new blood refers to a group of gulf cartel operative who have turn against the zetas as member of the organization bid to control traffic route and local drug market .
mexico 's secretary of public safety genaro garcia luna say in may 2007 that the gulf cartel have split into rival band .
garcia luna say in a recent press conference that the extreme violence in mexico be part of a strategy by drug trafficker to force authority into a strategic retreat .
garcia luna say that they be try to create a climate of intimidation and fear in order to gain operational advantage .
luna say the resident of a rural town or urban neighborhood will refuse to cooperate with authority and create a social space of support for trafficker if they believe that drug trafficker cannot be defeat .
gruesome killings have become frequent during the war this year .
new incident of violence have arise every day this week .
authority on june 6 , 2007 discover a decapitate body leave with a write message for state police in the port city of veracruz on the gulf of mexico .
the message say police be protect rival drug trafficker and that the decapitated man have be sell drug for a rival group .
four other people be kill in and around veracruz that same day .
this include a funeral director who have transport the body of efrain torres to a cemetery in the city of poza rica in may .
torres be an assassinate leader of the zetas .
the body later be steal from its crypt .
another victim of the violence in veracruz cannot yet be tally among the dead .
business owner roberto moguel martinez be kidnap by arm men on june 6 , 2007 after be release from a hospital .
martinez have be recover from wound suffer in a may 31 , 2007 attack .
martinez 's mother wrestle briefly with martinez 's arm kidnapper on a street in the center of the city accord to the veracruz newspaper notiver .
martinez have not be see since .
on june 7 , 2007 there be three grenade attack on two police station and an army barrack in the southern state of guerrero .
authority say seven people be kill in apparent drug @-@ related attack there .
the websites of mexico city newspaper on june 8 , 2007 report as many as 20 people have be gunned down nationwide in drug @-@ related violence the previous 24 hour .
the dead include three people shot on a highway in the state of durango in northwest mexico .
this happen on a week when president felipe calderon traveled to europe to meet with pope benedict xvi and other leader .
calderon tell reporter on june 4 , 2007 in rome that consumer in the unite state be to blame for the drug @-@ driven chaos in mexico .
calderon say that this be a share problem between the unite state and mexico .
the principal cause be the use of drug .
and the u.s. be the prime consumer in the world .
calderon have send the army to numerous mexican state to fill in for over @-@ match and corrupt local police .
19 member of the army be order on june 4 , 2007 to be imprison as suspect in the kill of three women and two children at a rural anti @-@ smuggle checkpoint in sinaloa .
the five be member of a family return from a wake .
military official say they have fail to stop at the checkpoint .
the shoot be more evidence of the war @-@ like psychology grip many corner of mexico .
an estimate 1,200 people be already kill in the violence this year .
