when meet with the governor of macao viera here today , premier of the state council peng li say the policy of the chinese government towards macao be consistent , firm and unchanging , and that the chinese government would , in accordance to the policy of " one country , two system " and strictly accord to the regulation in the joint declaration between china and portugal and the basic law of macao , maintain the stability and development of macao .
peng li express welcome at the periodic visit of viera .
he say : " in recent year , the friendly co @-@ operative relationship between the two country namely china and portugal in various arena have be develop continuously , mutual visit by top level leader of both country have also increase .
president zemin jiang , vice president yiren rong and myself have all visit portugal , and prime minister shewar visit china in april of this year . "
