peng li point out , the macao issue be an important component of the relationship between china and portugal .
maintain good relationship between the two country of china and portugal , as well as the inland and macao , be beneficial for the social stability and economic development .
peng li say since the joint declaration between china and portugal come into effect , both side have do quite a lot of work in the thorough implementation of the joint declaration , and that co @-@ operation have be effective .
in recent year , under the joint effort of both side , many issue of mutual concern to both side have be resolve , various degree of progress have be achieve in the three major issue , namely language , civil servant , and law in the transition period of macao .
he say : " we hope that the macao government will continue to give their attention to these three problem , in order to achieve final proper resolution . "
peng li say , " governor viera have do a lot of beneficial work in the smooth resolution of the macao issue , for this we express our appreciation . "
