both side should resolve the outstanding issue in the spirit of friendly consultation .
he hope that the macao government would further strengthen the consultation and co @-@ operation with the chinese side on the major issue regard the stable transition of macao and the smooth hand over of political power , in a way that would be beneficial to the stability and development of macao .
peng li say : " we believe , through the friendly co @-@ operation and joint effort of both the chinese and portuguese side , the stable transition and smooth hand over of the political power would definitely be realize .
viera happily recall the two meeting he have with premier peng li in 1991 and 1992 , and highly assess the important contribution make by the chinese government and premier peng li himself in the development of the relationship between portugal and china and the resolution of the macao issue .
viera say , he be glad to see that china have achieve great progress in the area of economic and social life , and express complete understand that the modernization build - up need to be carry out under stable situation .
he say , the stability and development of china be beneficial to world peace and development , and that the prosperity and stability of china be the basic guarantee for the prosperity and stability of macao .
he and the portuguese government would continue to put forth effort towards the continuous development and smooth resolution of the macao issue .
