xinhua news agency , beijing , august 31 st , by reporter jie sun
china 's chemical industry be accelerate the pace of open up to the outside world , and stride into the world .
accord to ministry of chemical industry presentation , total chemical import and export in china be less than 300 million us dollar in 1978 , reach 7.5 billion us dollar last year , and there be already 30 chemical enterprise who export foreign exchange surpass 10 million us dollar .
complete equipment set export of china 's chemical industry make a fractional breakthrough , while double equipment set installation , with an annual production of 40,000 ton of ion film caustic soda , be successively export to indonesia and complete equipment set , with an annual production of 200,000 ton of sodium carbonate , be export to iran .
technology export also make new progress .
currently , technology export that china can provide reach 52 .
accord to incomplete statistic , in the past 3 year , china export more than 20 technology , such as anthraquinone hydrogen peroxide solution , variable voltage absorption , etc .
up to the first half of this year , china 's ministry of chemical industry sign co @-@ operation agreement with 15 large international chemical corporation .
in the past ten year , foreign capital that china 's chemical industry accumulatively absorb reach 8.5 billion us dollar , and be be use for the construction and technology transformation of chemical fertilizer and petroleum .
