xinhua news agency , nanjing , april 23 rd , by reporter futian yang
zijin mountain observatory of the china academy of science announce today that a nation - wide observation network for the collision of shoemaker - levy 9 comet with jupiter have be build in china and a large - scale astronomical observation plan have be formulate as well .
accord to expert , jupiter , which orbit the sun like the earth , be the largest planet in the solar system .
this incident of observe of the comet collide with jupiter possess extremely important significance in research and forecast comet collide with earth .
the chinese astronomy arena also place great importance on this phenomenon of the comet collide with jupiter and will closely focus attention on its development and change .
in the past few day , under the support of the chinese academy of science and the national natural science foundation , a seminar on the plan to monitor comet shoemaker - levy 9 collide with jupiter convene in nanjing and more than forty astronomer from all over the country attend .
expert think that this rare and important astronomical phenomenon require continuous global observation , and that china be locate at an important longitudinal position between japan and europe , so , china 's observational material from be an indispensable and irreplaceable component in the international joint observation .
at that time , china will put all advanced astronomical equipment to use to carry out observation , include 2.16 - meter reflect telescope , 1.26 - meter infrared telescope and radio telescope .
25 - meter telescope in the decimeter and centimeter wave band , 10 - meter wave band telescope and advanced optical telescope terminal equipment will also be use .
nanjing zijin mountain observatory have more than forty year of experience in the observation and research of comet and asteroid , and its planet research office be the only scientific research organization in china conduct long term research on comet and asteroid , and since 1988 also start research the issue of the solar system 's celestial body collide .
this station 's planet expert also attend many international scientific seminar on the danger of comet and asteroid collide with earth .
( end )
