xinhua news agency , moscow , august 31 , by reporter rong xie
russia 's last group of personnel that should withdraw of the northwest military troop station in the three country of the baltic sea completely withdraw from latvia on the 31 st .
until now , russia have complete the troop withdrawal work from the three country of baltic sea .
it be report by news media here that on the 31 st , the personnel of the russian northwest troop headquarters turn over military installation to the local government , submit a report to latvian president ulmanis regard the completion of troop withdrawal , and then withdraw from riga to moscow by plane .
russian troop station in lithuania already withdraw back home before august 31 st of 1993 , and troop station in estonia complete troop withdrawal work on the 29 th of this month .
accord to agreement reach by russia with the government of latvia and estonia , currently there be still a few hundred russian military expert remain in the early warn radar station of the latvian and russian naval education centers in estonia .
the russian northwest troop cluster be former soviet troop station in the above three country , with headquarters set in the latvian republic .
the total original military strength be more than 116,000 people , within which most , more than 50,000 people , be station in latvia ; more than 35,000 people in lithuania , and more than 30,000 people in estonia .
after the disintegration of the former soviet union , these troop cluster be transfer to russian ownership .
it be report that the russian troop that withdraw from the three baltic sea country will be station respectively in the russian state of jalininggele , the state of simolingsike and yelinia city which be 300 kilometers away from moscow .
( end )
